4. Login as a DEFAULT_USER
5. Verify user is logged in successfully
6. Create a new post with Title "New test title" and Body Content "New text for the test"
7.Verify the post was created successfully

Steps:
1. Click on My Profile icon
2. Click on post with Title "New test title"
3. Verify the post with Title "New test title" was opened -> Delete and edite icons are shown, title of the post is "New test title"
4. Click on the Delete icon

Expected Result:
1. Verify the post was deleted and user sees the message "Post successfully deleted" on the Home Page. The Posts counter is changed, deleted post is not shown anymore.

Post-conditions:
1. Delete user USER_NAME from the system

